	MaskedMan: Yes.[pause=0.2] It would bring me much joy.
	update Bella (look)
	Bella: I suppose I will have to find a way...
	Bella: I still have this knife...
	set {level3_first_interaction_with_man} = true
elif {level3_door_opened} == true:
	MaskedMan: Proceed forward,[pause=0.2] and good riddance.
elif {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature1} == false and {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature2} == false and {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature3} == false:
	MaskedMan: Do not waste my time.
else:
	if {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature1} == true and {level3_told_secret1} == false:
		MaskedMan: Argh...
		update MaskedMan (happy)
		MaskedMan: You decimated my minion on the left.[pause=0.2] How utterly [pause=0.2][i]ruthless[/i].
		update MaskedMan (default)
		MaskedMan: Fine,[pause=0.2] I will tell you this.
		MaskedMan: You were a wonderful liar.[pause=0.2] You could convince a man that he was a cow.
		MaskedMan: It was really quite a feat.
		MaskedMan: I would even go as far as to say that you told lies more than truths.
		update Bella (serious)
		Bella: So that's why...
		Bella: I really was a liar.[pause=0.2] And a good one at that.
		update Bella (shock)
		Bella: That's terrible.
		set {level3_told_secret1} = true
	if {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature2} == true and {level3_told_secret2} == false:
		MaskedMan: Ugh.[pause=0.2] You destroyed my minion up above.
		update MaskedMan (happy)
		MaskedMan: Wonderful...
		update MaskedMan (default)
		MaskedMan: I suppose I could tell you this.
		MaskedMan: You were much like me,[pause=0.2] girl.
		MaskedMan: Always putting on a mask.[pause=0.2] Always pretending to be something you weren't.
		MaskedMan: Always figuring out the next way to get exactly what you wanted.
		update MaskedMan (happy)
		MaskedMan: It was beautiful.
		update Bella (shock)
		Bella: Pretending to be something I'm not?
		update Bella (look)
		Bella: It seems even in life,[pause=0.2] I didn't know who I was.[pause=0.2] How could I when I was always pretending to be someone else?
		update Bella (question)
		Bella: Why was I like that?[pause=0.2] Why did I need to manipulate people?
		set {level3_told_secret2} = true
	if {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature3} == true and {level3_told_secret3} == false:
		update MaskedMan (happy)
		MaskedMan: Ah![pause=0.2] You dispatched of my minion to the right!
		MaskedMan: It was quite beautiful to watch!
		update MaskedMan (default)
		MaskedMan: Let me tell you this,[pause=0.2] girl.
		MaskedMan: You came from a [pause=0.2][i]very[/i][pause=0.2] rich family.[pause=0.2] Those are the best kind.
		MaskedMan: Being born rich prevented you from being held down by the chains of[pause=0.2]...ugh[pause=0.2]...'empathy'.
		MaskedMan: You treated those the way they deserved.[pause=0.2] But you did so in a way that somehow made you seem [pause=0.2]'good'.
		update MaskedMan (happy)
		MaskedMan: It was really quite genius!
		update MaskedMan (default)
		MaskedMan: You would've done anything to maintain your status.
		MaskedMan: From doing whatever you could to become more beautiful.
		MaskedMan: To spreading lies to tear down others.
		update Bella (shock)
		Bella: That's...[pause=0.2] horrible...
		set {level3_told_secret3} = true
	if {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature1} == true and {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature2} == true and {level3_defeated_small_masked_creature3} == true:
		update Bella (look)
		Bella: I'm not sure I want to know anymore.
		update Bella (sad)
		Bella: I...[pause=0.2]I was horrible.
		update MaskedMan (happy)
		MaskedMan: You were magnificent!
		update MaskedMan (mad)
		MaskedMan: But now?[pause=0.2] You're only a hollow shell of what you once were.
		Bella: ...
		update MaskedMan (default)
		MaskedMan: You don't have to go on.
		update Bella (look)
		Bella: I have to.[pause=0.2] I was horrible.
		update Bella (serious)
		Bella: And yet...[pause=0.2]I still want to know how I died.
		update MaskedMan (mad)
		MaskedMan: Tch.[pause=0.2] Annoying.
		update MaskedMan (default)
		MaskedMan: Fine.[pause=0.2] I shall open the way so you can learn more.
		MaskedMan: Proceed forward,[pause=0.2] and good riddance.
		set {level3_door_opened} = true
		[signal arg="level3_door_opened"]
	else:
		MaskedMan: I still have more to tell if you are willing to prove yourself.

leave --All--
